Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.73,1:24:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.89,1:24:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.89,1:24:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
